    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That sounds like a good pivot, but what if a journalist digs deeper? If they ask specifically how an \"audit\" ended up having user emails visible to the public, how do we answer that without admitting it was an S3 bucket error? I don't want to get caught in a lie if they start asking for technical specifics.",
