      "content": "staged data... okay. but won't that look even more suspicious if they find out it was actually just a basic permission setting error on the bucket? i'm worried that if we're too \"technical\" with this explanation and it gets debunked by a tech reporter, the backlash for being dishonest will be way worse than if we just admitted it was a small mistake. are you sure this is the safest way to protect the brand?",
